doctype html5
html
  head
    title Twidd.ly
    link(rel="stylesheet", type="text/css", href="style.css")
  body
    header
      img(src="images/twiddlyLogo.png")
    main
      section#title
        .story
          img(src="images/phoneLock1.png", alt="")
          .caption
            h2 Transcend Boredom
            p Twiddly brings the best of the web, right to your lockscreen
      section#curated
        .story
          .caption
            h2 Stories that inspire you
            p Choose from curated themes to get handpicked stories you'd enjoy.
          img(src="images/phoneThemes.png", alt="")
      section#lockscreen
        .story
          img(src="images/phoneLock2.png", alt="")
          .caption
            h2 Dive right in
            p Read articles, watch videos and browse stories without unlocking your phone.
      section#snacky
        .story
          img(src="images/phoneLock2.png", alt="")
          .caption
            h2 Stories that pack a punch
            p Snack away on stories that are no longer than 5 minutes!
      section#founders
        .section-title
          h4 The Founders
        .story
          .container
            img(src="images/ranjan.jpg", alt="")
            .caption
              h3.right Ranjan Jagannathan
              p.right Ranjan most recently led customer development, product experiments and analytics for a 500 Startups company, Mygola. Before Mygola, Ranjan was an innovation program manager with Yahoo! India where he designed and ran large scale innovation programs. Ranjan has a degree in Mechanical Engineering and is an alum of Stanford Ignite, an academic program on entrepreneurship by Stanford Graduate School of Business.
          .container
            .caption
              h3.left Sanjay Guruprasad
              p.left Sanjay graduated from IIT Madras in 2012 where he was awarded the Institute Blues for his wide ranging pursuits on campus. He worked at an iBank for a year, but decided to return to Bangalore to chase his startup dream. He worked as a full stack developer at MagnetWorks, developing an alerts system for the iOT startup. He headed 'Enerji', a NodeJS project at Softrade that helps factories move to cleaner fuels. He loves NodeJS, iOS and is very into minimalism.
            img(src="images/sanjay.jpg", alt="")
      section#signup-form
        .section-title
          h1 Sign Up!
        form(id="signup", method="POST", action="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1dv0Ow2ik-zTlLn3y6qdMje04sjUypou5P16F1r4pb7I/formResponse")
          .info
            p Twiddly is coming to your lockscreen soon!
            p.hug Get early access by signing up for the beta below.
          select(name="entry.1200618361", id="entry_1200618361", placeholder="Choose Phone", required)
            option(default) Which phone do you own?
            option iPhone
            option Windows
            option Other
            option Android
          input(name="entry.1422492071", id="entry_1422492071", placeholder="Email address", required)
          button(type="submit", name="submit", value="Submit") Sign up for a sneak peak!

  footer


